üî• Ultra-Short Last-Minute Revision
Jobs parallel, steps sequential
360 min max job runtime
Step timeout > job timeout
fail-fast default true (matrix)
cancel-in-progress default false
Fresh VM per job
Secrets masked
Least privilege permissions


