2Ô∏è‚É£0Ô∏è‚É£ Best Practices (High-Value Interview Points)

Use needs for job dependencies

Pin action versions

Use OIDC instead of cloud secrets

Use concurrency for deployments

Use caching to reduce pipeline time

Avoid secrets in logs

Separate CI and CD workflows


